              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Ilford C.2 plates, with emulsion thicknesses",
                "of 100 mum"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A Li-6 target was used. The thickness of the Li-6",
                "specimen was estimated to be equivalent to an energy",
                "loss of 50 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By author*. The resulting neutron spectra are shown",
                "in figures 1 and 2, where each ordinate is proportional",
                "to the number of neutrons in an energy interval of",
                "0.1 MeV. The scale has been chosen to make the ordinate",
                "equal to the number of proton tracks observed in the",
                "interval 3.15-3.25 MeV. At higher energies the",
                "ordinates are greater and at lower energies less than",
                "the numbers of tracks from which they are obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
